#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Phone" field of the "Distributor" table</h2>
This field is the primary phone number for the distribution center.  It is in the format:
    <div class=field_format>(nnn)nnn-nnnn</div>
It currently isn't used by the software but is here for completeness sake.  It is usually
the phone number of the meal coordinator.

